Name: Average time for Queued + Awaiting Assignment across all process variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in Queued + Awaiting Assignment before transitioning to Accepted + In Progress
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Minimum time required to complete Queued + Awaiting Assignment when followed by Accepted + Wait - User
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Average duration of Queued + Awaiting Assignment in variants that include Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Total time from the start of a case to the completion of Queued + Awaiting Assignment
Metric: The sum of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Minimum time elapsed from Queued + Awaiting Assignment to Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average cycle time of Queued + Awaiting Assignment when it appears multiple times in the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Total duration of Queued + Awaiting Assignment in variants that end with Completed + Closed without passing through Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + Closed occurs

Name: Average time for Queued + Awaiting Assignment grouped by country
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Total time spent in Queued + Awaiting Assignment before the first occurrence of Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Minimum time for Queued + Awaiting Assignment in variants containing Accepted + Wait - Vendor
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Average time from Queued + Awaiting Assignment to Completed + Resolved when Completed + In Call is not present
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total time between consecutive occurrences of Queued + Awaiting Assignment within the same case
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Average duration of Queued + Awaiting Assignment in cases handled by resources in Brazil compared to France
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and the end of case grouped by the last value of resource country

Name: Time elapsed from case start to Queued + Awaiting Assignment in variants that later include Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between the beginning of the case and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' for cases where activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' occurs

Name: Average time for Queued + Awaiting Assignment when immediately followed by Accepted + Assigned
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Total time spent in Queued + Awaiting Assignment across all variants that contain more than one instance of this activity
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Minimum time required to exit Queued + Awaiting Assignment when the next activity is Accepted + In Progress
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average time between the last Queued + Awaiting Assignment and Completed + In Call in multi-assignment variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + In Call'
